                </p>
                <ol style="padding-left: 20px; ">
                    <li>Stop the behavior in progress through distraction.</li>
                    <li>Redirect her to an alternate, approved activity.</li>
                    <li>Reward the good behavior with a treat, affection or brief playtime.</li>
                </ol>
